(74, 'BusinessEditCoke', 'Coke', 'Group has grown manifolds since its inception and has expanded its presence in Coke manufacturing and export of coke along with Coal trading. Group currently own four coke manufacturing units in India.<br/><br/>\r\n<b> Mahalaxmi Group</b> has expertise in manufacturing and supplying an encompassing assortment of LAM Coke, Met Coke, Pearl Coke, and Coke Breeze and thereby aims to establish a strong foothold in the industry by fabricating a quality array of products, which conform to the international quality standards.<br/><br/>\r\nWe have started exporting our Coke Consignment across the globe; Recently, we have completed our 3rd consignment of Coke Export with its high resistance, strength, texture & efficiency.', 'https://nsws.in.net/development/mahalaxmi/version10/index.php?page=Energy', '98222b98a2b50ade40d9631a43865e14.png', '', 'f722c26929e746f613067da467919611.png', '69a13c28a10141a26d82091640b7b76a.png', 'c3031a8cee0cfcfabfa7866fe865d07b.png', 'c88395ffa2eaaeb091bd0a3c68c25617.png', 'Quantity <br/> 2 Lakhs + MT', 'Value <br/> 600 Crore', 'Plant <br/> 4', 'Production <br/> Self', 'd7f39d2fda250c5e0f5d69f40d029f57.png', 'ce27ccb7d3260914f54beb2e3448055d.png', 'Active'),
(75, 'BusinessEditMining', 'Mining', 'Our flagship company Mahalaxmi Mining Pvt. Ltd., is assigned in Nagaland, India, to extract coal in the area.\r\n<br/><br/> In addition, we are joint venturing with the leading mining companies of the country for undertaking major mining works in the North-Eastern states of India and other states as well through which we endeavour to create high value for customers, which would be evident with our strong distribution network and customer service.', 'https://nsws.in.net/development/mahalaxmi/version10/index.php?page=Energy', '38e3494325025b2994b4b1c76b1a8d06.png', '', 'd8e76cb920690e831d6ff82c66c6f7bd.png', 'a145c76328c4b1fe08572cfa3262cf82.png', '10695c07889377e5b49d4a4c9fe658f4.png', '882a03272fcc6f9af093f4a0220456d4.png', '', '', '', '', '5d7a6f25e7e46720363f18a0efe8ba74.png', NULL, 'Active'),
