(1, 'csr_header', 'Corporate Social Responsibility', NULL, 'cf779e42fdc92b5bedbb1d71c0728468.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Active'),
(2, 'csr_description', NULL, 'The main idea behind Corporate Social Responsibility (CSR) is that a business has a responsibility to the society around it. Beside regulatory compliance, our CSR is driven by our moral convictions and the belief that CSR can bring multiple benefits.<br/><br/> \r\n\r\nOur CSR revolves around the United Nations Industrial Development Organisation (UNIDO) concept of Triple Bottom Line (TBL) approach: \"profit, people, and planet\". This has been found to be an efficient tool for companies in developing nations to comply with social and environmental norms while maintaining their competitiveness.<br/><br/>\r\nOur CSR activities are directed towards contributing towards the UN Sustainable Development Goals. Following the United Nations Industrial Development Organisation (UNIDO) guidelines, we integrate social and environmental concerns in our business operations and interactions with stakeholders.\r\n <br/><br/>\r\nOur CSR targets the whole value chain from suppliers to operations to partners to end-consumers while fulfilling our business purposes. To us, <b>CSR is compliance</b>. Sustainability is about business. CSR gets managed by communications teams. <br/><br/>\r\nWe have established a social welfare organization named “<b>Mahalaxmi Foundation</b>” and <b>Nav Jeevan Foundation</b> to serve society. The foundation actively supports the poor and needy people and works for the upliftment of the deprived class of the society through monetary donations and aid given to non-profit organizations and communities in areas such as education, health, food, livelihood, housing, sports, etc. <br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<b>Collaborative partnerships</b> are formed with the Government, the District Authorities, the village panchayats, NGOs, and other like-minded stakeholders for taking the CSR mission forward.\r\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Active'),
(3, 'csr_facts', '<p>As a environment conscious company, we have been striving to use the best practices in reduction of pollution through use of latest innovations in the field, tree plantation, water conservation, waste management and power reduction.</p>\r\n', '<p>The group has developed excellent process for ethical and fair treatment of its employees through regulatory compliance of working conditions and labour standards. Continuous efforts are maintained for community relations, social and cultural equity and gender balancing in work life. Regular efforts are made for participation in local causes.</p>\r\n', '<p>Philanthropic responsibility refers to a business&#39;s commitment to actively contribute to the improvement of the world and society.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Along with acting ethically and sustainably, we are motivated by charitable duty and frequently donate to the cause of food, housing, education, health care, poverty, and sports.</p>\r\n', '768a60a3728a611abb59d56dbaf9f6c0.png', '18614356ece2a9adbeea84ae5eee293e.png', 'e8c13208bf54ef799ba9712e1a1f98a1.png', 'b8d3afd8b9fe78dcb4bf653e7728a8a0.png', 'bed444c25779978fb18b5ce33882b085.jpg', '518a62090552aa89ec85d6449b9f20df.png', 'b5b951d8eb0cda75e04e473aaf7e7120.jpg', '1aac6f0727734d4e7cbd4487aab857a1.png', 'Environment', 'Society', 'Safety', 'Economic', '<p>Economic responsibility is the practice of underpinning all of our financial actions with a desire to do good in the aforementioned areas. The ultimate objective is not profit maximization, but rather to have a good influence on the environment, people, and society.</p>\r\n', 'Active'),
