(15, 'Team_Directors', 'Vipin Singhal', 'Administration, Director', 'b878f333368cc9c7dc3839fd65f9206a.jpg', 'Mr. Vipin Singhal is a commerce graduate with more than 15 years of experience. He actively contributes towards solving issues related to business and trade in general. He also leads the Administrative wing of the group and is responsible for the successful outcome of all related tasks.', NULL, 'Active'),
(16, 'Team_Directors', 'Bimal Kumar Agarwal', 'Commercial, Director', '5c2829172571003ae191827a3461502e.jpg', 'With more than 30 years of experience, Mr. Bimal Kumar Agarwal has led project managements across many industries with specialty in Coke manufacturing, Supply Chain Operation and Quality Control. He also has rich and diverse experience in Iron Ore, Cement and Steel industry and has been responsible for commissioning several Coke Plants in the North Eastern India.', NULL, 'Active'),
(17, 'Team_Directors', 'Budh Ram Bansal', 'Head Business Associate', '976c82359d1033274690d73e31bef673.jpg', 'A commerce graduate with more than 40 years of experience in coal industry. Mr. Budh Ram Bansal\'s dedication and precise approach has always been helpful in creating \"Win-Win\" situation for the group.', NULL, 'Active'),
(18, 'Team_Directors', 'Avdesh Singhal', 'Director, Logistics', 'bb4b5168b04b5198caa84e08fc165944.jpg', 'A commerce graduate with expertise in business logistics, Mr. Avdhesh has played a key role in the development of its Coal trading business since 1998. He is actively involved in coordination of projected requirement, procurement, and physical movement to achieve optimum demand-service level at minimal cost. It includes both inbound and outbound movements.', NULL, 'Active'),
(19, 'Team_Directors', 'Bal Kishan Bansal', 'Director, Universal Infraworld Ltd.', '5a28b27c2b5d526379d53ef4a4135ead.jpg', 'Mr. Bal Kishan Bansal, a Chartered Accountant, has been associated with the group since 1992 and leads the Real Estate & Infrastructure division under the banner of Universal Infraworld Pvt. Ltd. He has more than 10 years of experience in the field of Construction industry and has led several large construction projects across North Eastern India. He also has vast experience in the field of accountancy, finance and legal consultancy.', NULL, 'Inactive'),
(20, 'Team_Directors', 'Anil Kumar Agarwal', 'Director, Personal', 'a194be43fdbc1aef73f9ac24d28a00f6.jpg', 'Mr. Anil Kumar Agarwal has been associated with the group since 2008. He leads our Coke manufacturing division with vigor and determination. He has worked in diverse industries including steel & mining, agricultural products as well as soft and hard commodities.', NULL, 'Inactive'),
(21, 'Team_Directors', 'Sandeep Bharat', 'Director', 'dee6398a42bfa8affdf174fa32af5fd1.jpg', 'Sandeep Bharat is a seasoned professional with a diverse career spanning over 18 years. He holds a Master of Computer Applications (MCA) degree, which laid the foundation for his successful entry into the IT industry. Sandeep spent approximately nine years working with leading IT companies such as Infosys and Yahoo, where he honed his skills in various aspects of technology and project management. His tenure in these companies was marked by significant contributions to numerous high-profile projects, showcasing his expertise and dedication.\r\n<br/><br/>\r\nAfter a fruitful career in IT, Sandeep ventured into the import and export business, where he has been actively involved for the past nine years. As a Director in this sector, he has developed expertise in coal and coke procurement from various sources, operations, shipping, and international business. His leadership has been instrumental in driving growth and fostering strong relationships with international partners, effectively applying his technical knowledge and strategic thinking to navigate the complexities of global trade and establish a robust and successful business.\r\n<br/><br/>\r\nOutside of his professional endeavors, Sandeep is passionate about traveling. His love for exploring new places enriches his life with diverse experiences and broadens his perspective. Additionally, Sandeep enjoys spending quality time with his team, believing that strong interpersonal relationships and teamwork are key to achieving success. His approachable nature and enthusiasm for collaboration make him a valued leader and colleague in any setting.', NULL, 'Active');
